    • 枚举常量概要

      枚举常量 
      枚举常量和说明
      DISCONNECTED
      the switch has disconnected, and will soon be removed from the switch database
      HANDSHAKE
      this switch is in the process of being handshaked.
      MASTER
      the OF channel to this switch is currently in MASTER (or EQUALS) role - the switch is controllable from this controller node.
      QUARANTINED
      the switch has been sorted out and quarantined by the handshake.
      SLAVE
      the OF channel to this switch is currently in SLAVE role - the switch will not accept state-mutating messages from this controller node.

      • HANDSHAKE

        public static final IOFSwitch.SwitchStatus HANDSHAKE

      • SLAVE

        public static final IOFSwitch.SwitchStatus SLAVE
        the OF channel to this switch is currently in SLAVE role - the switch will not accept state-mutating messages from this controller node.

      • MASTER

        public static final IOFSwitch.SwitchStatus MASTER

      • QUARANTINED

        public static final IOFSwitch.SwitchStatus QUARANTINED

      • DISCONNECTED

        the switch has disconnected, and will soon be removed from the switch database
